'''圣心主教座堂'''是[[天主教拉合尔总教区|天主教拉合尔总教区]]的[[主教座堂|主教座堂]]，位于[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[拉合尔|拉合尔]]。1907年11月19日祝圣<ref>{{cite web |title = Pastoral Letter Of Archbishop Lawrence Saldanha |url = http://www.archdioceselahore.org/plcatcen.htm |access-date = 2014-06-18 |archive-date = 2022-01-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220125194137/http://www.archdioceselahore.org/plcatcen.htm |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。其风格为罗曼拜占庭式，设计者为比利时[[安特卫普|安特卫普]]建筑师Dubbeleere博士。<ref>{{cite web |title = A SACRED LANDMARK REACHES 100 |url = http://www.archdioceselahore.org/prccn07.doc |access-date = 2014-06-18 |archive-date = 2022-01-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220125194137/http://www.archdioceselahore.org/prccn07.doc |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。 

在该堂的百年庆典之际，巴基斯坦邮政总局发行了纪念邮票<ref>Pakistan Press International November 20, 2007</ref><ref>{{cite web |title = Sacred Heart Cathedral celebrates its first 100 years |url = http://www.asianews.it/index.php?l=en&art=10845 |accessdate = 2014-06-18 |archive-date = 2019-08-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190810150429/http://www.asianews.it/index.php?l=en&art=10845 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，教廷大使也宣读教宗诏书。 

2008年3月11日，一名自杀式袭击者驾驶满载炸药的汽车闯进八层FIA办公楼，该堂至少有十扇花窗玻璃被毁<ref>{{cite web|title = UCANews.com March 14, 2008|url = http://www.ucanews.com/2008/03/14/a-day-of-terror/?key=sacred+heart+high+school++pakistan}}{{Dead link|date=2018年9月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

到2011年，该堂已经举行了2万多次洗礼和接近5,500次婚礼<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ucanews.com/2011/12/19/lahore-archdiocese-marks-125-years/ |title=UCANews December 19, 2011 |accessdate=2014年6月18日 |archive-date=2012年2月1日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120201194514/http://www.ucanews.com/2011/12/19/lahore-archdiocese-marks-125-years/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

